OL,6,FA private company has been chosen to
OL,7,Frun Jersey's popular Havre des Pas
OL,8,FLido on a nine-year lease, beginning
OL,9,Fat the start of 2026.
OL,11,FThe site is owned by the Government
OL,12,Fand Infrastructure Minister Connetable
OL,13,FAndy Jehan has signed a Ministerial
OL,14,FDecision confirming the intention to
OL,15,Fappoint First Point, a property
OL,16,Fmanagement company, to operate the
OL,17,Fpublic bathing pool.
