OL,6,FThis is despite public support behind
OL,7,Fthe 'Love Our Lido' community group,
OL,8,Fwho were previously named by St Helier
OL,9,FSouth Deputy David Warr as the
OL,10,Fpreferred bidder.
OL,12,FConnetable Jehan explains: "This
OL,13,Fagreement, following a thorough
OL,14,Fprocess, gives the Lido the fresh
OL,15,Fstart that everyone has recognised is
OL,16,Fneeded."
