OL,6,FSimon Crowcroft, Connetable for St
OL,7,FHelier, adds: "First Point are
OL,8,Fenthusiastic to put the needs of
OL,9,Fswimmers right at the top of the
OL,10,Fagenda for the lido.
OL,12,F"They want the terraces to be power-
OL,13,Fwashed daily, the children's pool to
OL,14,Fbe kept clean, decent changing
OL,15,Ffacilities, and the ability to get a
OL,16,Fhot drink all year round.
