OL,7,Fgroup says: "We have received no
OL,8,Fcommunication from government
OL,9,Fregarding this decision, their plans,
OL,10,For our future tenancy, nor have we had
OL,11,Fany contact from the responsible
OL,12,Fdepartment for over 12 months.
