OL,6,F"The only information we were aware of
OL,7,Fprior to today's reports was that a
OL,8,Fproposition to terminate the tender
OL,9,Fprocess had been lodged earlier this
OL,10,Fweek on the basis that its design was
OL,11,Ffundamentally at odds with the
OL,12,Fcommunity-led outcome it was intended
OL,13,Fto achieve and was being managed by
OL,14,Fthe very department the protest had
OL,15,Frequested to be removed.
OL,17,F"It is clear that the government has
OL,18,Ffailed the public through a flawed,
OL,19,Fopaque and divisive process that
OL,20,Fignores the will of the community."
