OL,6,FFirst Point were not the preferred
OL,7,Fbidder for the bathing pool, which in
OL,8,FJuly Deputy Warr announced as 'Love
OL,9,FOur Lido', a community-run venture led
OL,10,Fby local businessman Matt Falla.
OL,12,FHowever, this bid collapsed in late
OL,13,FSeptember after Deputy Warr says
OL,14,F"several fundamental issues" emerged,
OL,15,Fincluding concerns over a lack of
OL,16,Ffunding for maintenance and
OL,17,Foutstanding utility invoices, which
OL,18,Fcould have become the responsibility
OL,19,Fof the group's volunteers.
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                    G7/13
