OL,6,FIn their statement, Lido Jersey
OL,7,Fclaims: "The future charity governors
OL,8,Fof the lido have never pulled out of a
OL,9,Ftender process and are still waiting
OL,10,Fon clarity of financials from Jersey
OL,11,FProperty Holdings to proceed as
OL,12,Fresponsibly required as a registered
OL,13,Fcharity."
OL,15,FThis is at odds with Connetable
OL,16,FCrowcroft's view, as he explains:
OL,17,F"Love our Lido were the preferred
OL,18,Fbidder, but they pulled out of the
OL,19,Fprocess and insisted they would only
OL,20,Fstay in the process if the Government
OL,21,Fgave them more money.
