OL,7,Fwas happy to continue with the
OL,8,Fprevious criteria process.
OL,10,F"While this could have been a
OL,11,Fcommunity-led project, Love our Lido
OL,12,Fdidn't leave us any option after
OL,13,Fwithdrawing."
