OL,6,FDeputy Warr, Chair of the Lido
OL,7,FSteering Group, previously warned that
OL,8,Fmembers of the public would stage a
OL,9,Fprotest in early November "if
OL,10,Fmeaningful negotiations are not re-
OL,11,Fengaged" and says this option is still
OL,12,Fon the table following the
OL,13,FGovernment's announcement.
OL,15,FHe adds: "The saddest part of this
OL,16,Fdecision is that the group (First
OL,17,FPoint) haven't been around the
OL,18,Fcommunity or the Steering Group to
OL,19,Flisten to us, and establish what we'd
OL,20,Flike to happen.
