OL,6,F"I feel at this moment in time that
OL,7,Fthe whole process is predicated
OL,8,Fagainst coming up with the right
OL,9,Fsolution."
OL,11,FOn Wednesday, Deputy Warr submitted a
OL,12,Fproposition to Jersey States,
OL,13,Fdemanding the Government "terminate
OL,14,Fall ongoing negotiations and any
OL,15,Fassociated tender processes relating
OL,16,Fto the management, occupation or
OL,17,Fletting of the Havre des Pas Bathing
OL,18,FPool".
