OL,6,FThis motion will still be debated
OL,7,Fbefore the contract for the lido's
OL,8,Fmanagement is signed by First Point,
OL,9,Fmeaning it could be blocked by the
OL,10,Fisland's Deputies.
OL,12,FHowever, the Government says the
OL,13,Ftender process was fair and thorough,
OL,14,Fwith their decision offering the
OL,15,Fchance for new private investment
OL,16,Fwhile keeping the lido a community-
OL,17,Ffocused site.
OL,19,FConnetable Crowcroft has also defended
OL,20,Fthe choice and remains confident that
OL,21,Fthe takeover will not be delayed.
